<div class="row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-3 push">Google Spreadsheet Chart <br>
      <p class="push-text">The pros of this is that it is simple to execute, the main con is that this slows down load time
         as it now becomes dependent upon an outside resource.
      </p>
      <p>Resources:</p>
      <ul class="push-text">
        <li><%= link_to 'Create A Table of Data', scans_high_low_path, :target => "_blank" %></li>
